query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char, MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation FROM aka_name AS an, complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, info_type AS it, info_type AS it3, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, person_info AS pi, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND (k.keyword like '%dreams%' OR k.keyword like '%betrayal%') AND (mc.note like '%Germany%' OR mc.note like '%Italy%' OR mc.note like '%Russia%' OR mc.note like '%Sweden%') AND it3.info not in ('opening weekend','crazy credits','birth date','essays','LD disc size','LD picture format','production process protocol','adaption','keywords','LD language','LD pressing plant','countries','rentals','mini biography','article') AND (rt.role like '%Steve Harrison%') AND (an.name like '%p%' OR an.name like '%x%' OR an.name like '%S%') AND n.gender not in ('m') AND cct2.kind not in ('complete','cast') AND it.info in ('LD dynamic range','copyright holder','interviews','keywords','LD color information','birth name','mini biography') AND cct1.kind not in ('cast','crew','complete') AND cn.country_code not in ('dz','fo') AND mi.info in ('Czech','Rotuman','Slovak','Latin','Albanian','Kazakh','Brazilian Sign Language','Hungarian') AND (t.title like '%spell%' OR t.title like '%road%' OR t.title like '%light%' OR t.title like '%thriller%' OR t.title like '%picture%') AND chn.name not like '%Luke Skywalker%' AND (pi.note like '%IW%' OR pi.note like '%Samantha Mashaw%' OR pi.note like '%HH%')
